{"tid":1266724,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"覺得辛苦嘅我哋嚟聽歌吖不如 求你哋唔好傷害自己","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:59:36.000Z","uid":110018,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1b2f85d88d03d823ccbcc1b36bc10355810e33","tid":1266724,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"如果你呢刻情緒低落請你刻即刻搵人傾計<br />\n如果唔想傾計 希望你可以聽下歌 睇下戲<br />\n放鬆下 早啲休息<br />\n香港需要大家 戰友們請不要再退隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方皓玟 唵嘛呢叭咪吽<br />\n<br />\n當心生小念頭 別下手 挫折恐懼明天回走<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bzkGIyXiVCM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbzkGIyXiVCM&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=8894d842\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bzkGIyXiVCM</a><br />\n<br />\n方皓玟 假使世界原來不像你預期<br />\n<br />\n假使世界原來不像你預期 <br />\n仍懷著一顆謙卑 來面對不安的天氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BHeJdwCUAOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBHeJdwCUAOE&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=b283d2e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BHeJdwCUAOE</a><br />\n<br />\n張敬軒 Blessing<br />\n<br />\n種種愛是力量 帶動世上你與我的夢想<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n769TbKsT3M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn769TbKsT3M&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=ee1be8c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n769TbKsT3M</a><br />\n<br />\n張敬軒 缺<br />\n<br />\n這困局就用雙手來解脫<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FDi5TulrPG4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFDi5TulrPG4&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=ba58fa0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FDi5TulrPG4</a><br />\n<br />\nRubberband 發現號<br />\n<br />\n逆光中進發 不甘安置到盲點 上路再實踐<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wZD_qQ81l3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwZD_qQ81l3Q&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=4d15c275\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wZD_qQ81l3Q</a><br />\n<br />\nRubberband 逆流之歌<br />\n<br />\n拼了所有 斷氣方休<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l437aFu-29g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl437aFu-29g&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=6e99358e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l437aFu-29g</a><br />\n<br />\nShine 不怕<br />\n<br />\n世界太可怕 便強大到學會不怕<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mjCERO6gq9k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmjCERO6gq9k&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=81fd2e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mjCERO6gq9k</a><br />\n<br />\n謝安琪 雞蛋與羔羊<br />\n<br />\n一堆雞蛋望石牆 可以變做力場 繼續擴張<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R2_DWOyluTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR2_DWOyluTs&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=585b1589\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R2_DWOyluTs</a><br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment 沙燕之歌<br />\n<br />\n願你相信捱過明天的試煉<br />\n會在背後發現天際聚滿飛燕<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nsA3ue-hihE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnsA3ue-hihE&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=42001e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nsA3ue-hihE</a><br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment 無盡<br />\n<br />\n或許到最後沒有完美結局<br />\n仍然倔強冒險一一去征討<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4PACFmxlHm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4PACFmxlHm8&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=90274069\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4PACFmxlHm8</a><br />\n<br />\n林宥嘉 壞與更壞<br />\n<br />\n研習於失敗 維持歡快 才是崇高境界<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0MMhVTiiZDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0MMhVTiiZDI&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=7ff65eff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0MMhVTiiZDI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">急灣中成長嘅香港人 <br />\n其實我哋不斷進化緊㗎<br />\n請大家俾啲掌聲自己<br />\n就算呢刻好唔開心 <br />\n都請你唔好咁快認輸<br />\n我哋一定可以搵到個好嘅出口㗎！<br />\n支持住啊！<br />\n</span>"},{"p